          	  			<p data-element="content" class="content">A vest is one of the most versatile separates you can own, but you may need some ideas on how to wear this timeless wardrobe staple. Whether your vest is plain or decorated, and you want to wear it for day or night, we have a vested interest in helping you find the right style for you.</p>
